China May Announce Social Financing Target, Shanghai Daily Says

-- B y   J o s h u a   F e l l m a n
-- 
2011-03-03T20:08:15Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-03/china-may-announce-social-financing-target-shanghai-daily-says.html
  China  may announce a total social
financing target during the National People’s Congress meeting
that starts tomorrow, Shanghai Daily said, citing a Citibank
report.   The People’s Bank of China hasn’t disclosed the components
or targets for the new measure, meant to replace credit growth
as a target for monetary policy, the English-language newspaper
reported today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Joshua Fellman at 
 jfellman@bloomberg.net  